INSERT INTO `quest_offer_reward` (`ID`, `Emote1`, `Emote2`, `Emote3`, `Emote4`, `EmoteDelay1`, `EmoteDelay2`, `EmoteDelay3`, `EmoteDelay4`, `RewardText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES
(42679, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Outstanding. These new Ashtongue will give you the flexibility you need to position troops wherever you see fit.', 22594), -- 42679
(42670, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have selected your first two champions. There are great things ahead of us, $n.\n\n<Kor\'vas mutters something under her breath about not being one of them.>', 22594), -- 42670
(42697, 6, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 'You want me to be one of your champions?\n\n<Asha thoughtfully ponders your request a moment.>\n\nI accept, but on one condition. I want you to put me into field duty. While I am of use here on the Fel Hammer, my talents will be put to better use back on Azeroth.\n\nBeyond that, I trust that the plan is still to bring the Burning Legion to its knees?', 22594), -- 42697
(42690, 1, 274, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You honor me, $n. Of course I will serve as your champion and right-hand man. How could I refuse?\n\nWe have only just begun to change the way in which the Illidari operate, but already, you have made great strides. If we are to defeat the Burning Legion, it must be done in concert with everyone working together. Not just the Illidari standing alone.\n\nAnd not standing upon the smoking husk of a world that we have carelessly destroyed while trying to save it.', 22594), -- 42690
(42666, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Commander. I am glad to see that Asha was able to find you so quickly.\n\nThere is something important that you must attend to as soon as possible.', 22594), -- 42666
(39580, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Even without the hammer, I know what to do next. When our forces are rallied, we can take the fight to the Underking.', 22594), -- 39580
(40219, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'And so it was that Huln Highmountain came to this mountain, freeing the drogbar slaves of Deathwing, and came into possession of the Hammer of Khaz\'goroth.', 22594), -- 40219
(42622, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nice! Got \'em! Feel free to play the drums, but leave them down here, will you? You\'re alright by me, $n.', 22594), -- 42622
(40388, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am happy to see you, great ally.', 22594), -- 40388
(40112, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Eche\'ro looks up briefly, then lowers its head before you. This creature is thankful for your aid.>', 22594), -- 40112
(39983, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '[In broken Common] Feathered one said you come. Unng Ak not hope for you come. Tauren have thanks.', 22594), -- 39983
(40167, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have seen only a taste of what Huln Highmountain accomplished during his lifetime. Let us delve deeper into the past...', 22594), -- 40167
(39043, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Thank you for clearing us a path. We should have a straight shot at Dargrul now.', 22594), -- 39043
(44161, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well, at least we\'re going to have some fresh faces around here. If a broken\'s face can ever be called fresh, that is.\n\n<Kor\'vas smirks.>', 22594), -- 44161
(39579, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I always thought it odd that Ebonhorn never seemed to age. Or at least, he always looked old, but he never got older.', 22594), -- 39579
(39577, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'That day, the hammer freed me of the corruption of the Black Dragonflight.$b$bIn gratitude, I have faithfully served the Highmountain family since Huln rescued me from this pit.$b$bIt has been my honor and my pleasure to watch each of his descendants earn the title of High Chieftain.', 22594), -- 39577
(39578, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'And so Huln cast out Deathwing into the land of Deepholm and claimed the Hammer of Khaz\'goroth as his charge.$b$bBut there was one last bit of business for him to attend to...', 22594), -- 39578
(39575, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Quite a drop. Mind yourself in here, this is not a safe place.', 22594), -- 39575
(38916, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, thank you for coming. Mayla is as stubborn as her father if not more so.', 22594), -- 38916
(39992, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You see now, that Huln was mighty? He united the tribes and defeated terribly powerful foes.', 22594), -- 39992
(39990, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The ritual is complete. Reinforcements will be able to push through the portal and assist against the demonic hoard.', 22594), -- 39990
(39988, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You bring with you Eche\'ro, and... what is this? The blessing of Cenarius?!', 22594), -- 39988
(40520, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, these will be perfect for what is in store.', 22594), -- 40520
(39133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It has been a long time since the earth itself has moved against us like this.', 22594), -- 39133
(39134, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I suspect this is not the last of Dargrul\'s assaults. He is still learning the powers of the Hammer like a child with a new toy.', 22594), -- 39134
(40515, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You made Mayla smile. That is the first time I have seen her smile in... ever?', 22594), -- 40515
(38909, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Riverbend was... destroyed? That disgusting beast Dargrul! I will not stop until I see him dead.$b$bBut we cannot do that with the army we have.$b$bWe need help from the other tribes.', 22594), -- 38909
(39027, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oro and the others? Did they make it out as well?$b$bSuch destruction. So many good warbraves have fallen today.$b$bIt is clear now, we will need the full might of the Highmountain tribes if we are to recover the hammer.', 22594); -- 39027
